name: Insert Row Number in Prospect Algar
description: Insert Row Number in Prospect Algar otc291 filtrada
queryText:
select
a.cpf,
row_number() over(order by a.cpf) as row
from Tb_Base_Prospect_OTC291_Filtrada_Algar a
targetDescription: DE para insercao de contatos no Service e extracao para discador
